snippet.title: Elon Musk Set To Testify Against Amber Heard & Defend Johnny Depp
snippet.description:
Elon Musk Set To Testify Against Amber Heard & Defend Johnny Depp
Despite the court case between being Amber Heard and Johnny Depp primarily focusing on these two and how their marriage ended, the "circle of life" if you will didn't end there at all. Because throughout this court cases history, all sorts of celebs have been pulled in as either character witnesses, used to help get evidence across, and so on. And now, as we draw ever closer to the true court date for these two, some new celebrity witnesses are going to be taking the stand and handing over evidence. But why? We'll break it down for you. Be sure to like the video and subscribe to the channel!

Click HERE To Enter The GIVEAWAY! https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCbiT0LUIbQj6CQScvWHJeKQ?sub_confirmation=1

And there you have it, everyone! A look at the newest additions to the Amber Heard/Johnny Depp case and how they might just play a role in everything to come. Do you think that what is found with these two might go and change the court case entirely? Or will it just muddy the waters until it's hard to tell what the truth is or isn't? Let us know in the comments below, be sure to subscribe and we'll see you next time on the channel!
